reviewText: I can't say enough about this film. The skating is amazing and the photography is ahead of its time for skateboarding. I only wish drones were available back in the 90's. Simply beautiful film.

Stunning and breathtaking scenes the whole family will love. Settings range from gorgeous to dumps, skaters skate anywhere and everywhere in the world. This documentary includes heartwarming human interest and plenty of humor. A dazzling celebration of the sport. Terrific music too!
